<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/1411572-nicholas">Nicholas</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I wouldn&apos;t suggest this book to young adults (I&apos;m assuming that&apos;s what you mean?). Due to the time period it was written in, it is fairly problematic <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I wouldn't suggest this book to young adults (I'm assuming that's what you mean?). Due to the time period it was written in, it is fairly problematic and probably best for adults who know what they are getting into and can take everything with a grain of salt. <br /><br />Just my two cents.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
