<span id="freeTextContainer14500824821032991340">This is one of my all time favorite books. It is so &quot;latin&quot; in the sense that it supposes that passion and stability cannot co-exist except in an utterly unexpected way. I can&apos;t believe I am old enough to say I read it over twenty-something years ago. It was one my first forays into &quot;latin american literature&quot; and I must say it did not disappoint. A must read if you like passion and ghosts. </span>
